{"tid":1607402,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［水魔法］有一樣物資各位絲打都有，易入手又難洗","createTime":"2019-09-30T21:49:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T02:11:02.000Z","uid":310787,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1230e8512120482af54fe74737abee81eca17510","tid":1607402,"uid":310787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T21:49:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">就係你嘅粉底！！！！</span><br />\n<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n顏料貴 連埋水袋好易比狗周<br />\n唔知會唔會多人帶 <br />\n仲要細細枝 好快冇哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果個個女仔都帶枝粉底落街就唔怕冇啦</span><br />\n<br />\n痴過粉底落衫既都知 係有幾撚難洗<br />\n唔啱色唔好用過期嘅粉底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比人搜都唔怕啊 化妝犯法啊？<br />\n<br />\n拎枝冇用唇膏搽吓嘴仔 又得姐<br />\n齊齊整巫婆湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"281a8ece83cd24e1cc04cf65ca662792f985332c","tid":1607402,"uid":245030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T01:25:49.000Z","msg":"已帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然唔知得唔得 但帶咗先"},{"pid":"beae41b45b653ebf28af5b641c2384377fa83850","tid":1607402,"uid":142429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T01:59:53.000Z","msg":"又跟民權抗爭老將的法國朋友聊天，當然論及香港的反送中運動，朋友說，看到香港警察一身造價不菲的裝備，頭部更用非常堅固的頭盔完全包裹，鐵甲人一樣，非常安全，但他說，非常奇怪，香港的抗爭者竟然不會向這些防暴警頭盔的保護鏡投擲任何<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">顏料</span></strong>，個個防暴警的頭盔保護鏡竟然一塵不染。他說，投擲顏料相當容易，而保護鏡一旦看不清，就要把保護鏡拉起，甚至要卸下頭盔，自衛能力就大減，或要以真面目示人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Party差你一個炸 帶啲野黎啦</span></strong></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c4aae243af8409484a9f05075ae27b3cca035667","tid":1607402,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:11:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}